WEBVTT

00:03.940 --> 00:05.780
Oh, Hyde, get this.

00:05.860 --> 00:07.700
Casey just came by
to pick up Donna...

00:07.780 --> 00:10.580
and he was out in the street
just revving his Trans Am real loud...

00:10.660 --> 00:12.500
and then he peels out
in the street...

00:12.580 --> 00:14.780
and he started
doing doughnuts.

00:14.820 --> 00:17.300
And then, out comes Donna,
all smiling...

00:17.380 --> 00:20.380
and, like,
looking at him.

00:22.500 --> 00:24.900
What a slut!

00:24.980 --> 00:27.700
Look. If she wants
to date him, that's fine.

00:27.780 --> 00:30.540
But he doesn't have to be
all loud and jerky about it.

00:32.500 --> 00:34.740
Jerky, loud, doughnut jerk.

00:36.420 --> 00:39.060
Oh, guess what, boys.

00:39.140 --> 00:43.260
I entered the big wiener contest
at the Piggly Wiggly.

00:43.300 --> 00:48.580
And I won a year's supply
of all-beef hot dogs!

00:48.660 --> 00:52.020
I'm a wiener winner!

00:53.460 --> 00:55.580
Well, anyway,
we're having a barbecue.

00:55.620 --> 00:58.820
No, Kitty! I thought we were
going to talk about that.

00:58.900 --> 01:02.260
Mm-hmm. Oh, and I saw Donna
at the grocery store...

01:02.340 --> 01:04.220
and she said she's bringing
her friend Casey.

01:04.260 --> 01:06.940
What? No.
I hate Casey.

01:06.980 --> 01:10.140
He's Donna's new boyfriend.
Y-You have to uninvite him. Dad, tell her.

01:10.180 --> 01:13.820
Kitty, you've done
a horrible thing.

01:14.780 --> 01:17.180
It could scar the boy
for life.

01:17.260 --> 01:19.900
Now, let's do the right thing
and cancel that barbecue.

01:21.260 --> 01:23.580
No. We're having it,
and it'll be fun.

01:25.220 --> 01:29.500
And... we just...
We won't give Casey any relish.

01:33.340 --> 01:35.180
All right!

01:35.260 --> 01:39.220
Once Casey finds out he's not getting
any relish, he'll dump Donna for sure.

01:39.300 --> 01:41.660
You are so screwed.

01:48.680 --> 01:51.960
So your mom invited Casey
over for hot dogs?

01:52.040 --> 01:54.520
Well, that's a plump,
juicy all-beef burn.

01:57.040 --> 01:59.520
Ah, it's just typical
women stuff.

01:59.560 --> 02:02.240
Like Jackie
kissing that guy. Ow!

02:03.400 --> 02:05.440
- Hyde!
- Yeah. Okay?

02:05.480 --> 02:08.000
I've decided if anyone brings up
any more stupid girl stuff...

02:08.080 --> 02:10.720
I'm gonna throw something
at 'em.

02:10.800 --> 02:12.920
This time, I threw a fist.

02:14.040 --> 02:17.160
I'm sorry. It's just
everything reminds me.

02:17.240 --> 02:19.200
Like, last night <i>Rocky</i> was on...

02:19.240 --> 02:23.480
and I was thinking I'm like Rocky
and Jackie is Apollo Creed.

02:27.120 --> 02:31.880
And she bashed in my face
by kissing that guy!

02:31.960 --> 02:34.520
At least Rocky
wins in the end.

02:35.760 --> 02:37.840
Kelso, Rocky loses.

02:37.920 --> 02:42.560
Oh, yeah? Well, why is he
jumping around all happy?

02:42.600 --> 02:45.480
Because he goes
the distance, fool.

02:46.520 --> 02:50.320
He loses the fight,
but he wins in life.

02:51.720 --> 02:54.680
Who wants to watch a movie
with a message like that?

02:55.840 --> 02:58.920
Ice-cream man!

03:04.560 --> 03:08.000
You guys, I've been thinking
about Donna. And I...

03:08.040 --> 03:10.720
This time I threw a magazine.

03:10.760 --> 03:14.600
No, guys, seriously.
This barbecue might work out in my favor.

03:14.680 --> 03:18.800
You see, Donna's only seen Casey
around his smelly, tattooed...

03:18.880 --> 03:22.280
Molly Hatchet-lovin' friends.

03:22.360 --> 03:24.600
But when he comes to the barbecue,
he'll be around us...

03:24.680 --> 03:27.680
good, clean,
Lynyrd Skynyrd-lovin' Americans.

03:27.720 --> 03:31.160
And the comparison
will not be kind to him.

03:31.240 --> 03:33.920
And then Donna'll come
running home to you.

03:33.960 --> 03:35.840
No.

03:35.880 --> 03:37.920
Well, maybe.
You think?

03:38.000 --> 03:42.840
