highest authority on relationships.

05:18.760 --> 05:20.600
<i>Cosmo!</i>

05:24.000 --> 05:26.560
"Why you should touch
your breasts every day."

05:33.000 --> 05:35.240
No, this could help.
They seem smart.

05:39.480 --> 05:44.760
Okay, Fez, when Casey gets here, ask him
for advice about your second-base problem.

05:44.840 --> 05:48.120
My advice is gonna be
way better than his, and, uh...

05:48.200 --> 05:51.240
Donna will see that
he's a greasy dolt.

05:51.320 --> 05:53.920
Hey, Forman,
I have an idea.

05:54.000 --> 05:57.120
Set up a wacky system
of ropes and pulleys...

05:57.200 --> 06:00.440
and when Casey gets here,
drop an anvil on his head.

06:03.840 --> 06:06.800
- Because that's what Daffy does.
- Yeah, I got that.

06:09.960 --> 06:12.160
- Hey, guys.
- Hey.

06:12.200 --> 06:15.240
Hey, Foreplay.
Getting a little shaggy up there, buddy.

06:15.320 --> 06:17.640
Okay. Well, that's
enough of that!

06:17.720 --> 06:19.560
Okay.
So, uh...

06:19.640 --> 06:21.600
Hey, you guys
are just in time.

06:21.680 --> 06:25.280
Fez was telling me about, uh, some kind
of problem you're having with Rhonda.

06:25.360 --> 06:30.880
Yeah. Rhonda won't let me get past second
base, and I really want to explore further.

06:32.960 --> 06:36.680
Mmm. Gosh.
Well, I don't know...

06:36.760 --> 06:40.040
I think if you're patient,
and you're respectful...

06:40.080 --> 06:45.200
when Rhonda's ready,
she'll, uh... she'll wave you over.

06:45.280 --> 06:49.960
Well, thank you, Eric.
That is very gentlemanly advice.

06:52.440 --> 06:57.400
Gentlemanly?
Well, uh, guilty as charged, I guess.

07:00.760 --> 07:03.080
Hey, Casey, uh,
what do you think?

07:03.120 --> 07:07.320
Well, sometimes
a seasoned lady like Rhonda...

07:07.400 --> 07:10.400
she's gotten used to
the usual order of things.

07:10.440 --> 07:13.760
So, I think the next time
you're fooling around...

07:13.800 --> 07:17.600
just, uh, skip second
and go right to third.

07:17.640 --> 07:20.920
- What?
- It's genius!

07:21.000 --> 07:23.400
