you never get any.

07:26.760 --> 07:29.240
Yeah, with Rhonda, you know,
that just might work.

07:29.320 --> 07:31.360
W-Wait, you like that?

07:31.440 --> 07:35.280
Well, the words are wrong, but they
sound so good coming out of his mouth.

07:36.520 --> 07:39.040
I got a way about me.

07:43.160 --> 07:46.240
That worked out...
"thuper."

07:48.840 --> 07:53.040
Okay, Michael. I found something out
about our situation.

07:53.120 --> 07:56.960
This article says that cheating
is a symptom of a deeper problem.

07:57.000 --> 07:58.880
Deeper problem?

07:58.920 --> 08:02.960
