I want a quick fix!

08:03.040 --> 08:05.080
Well, too bad.

08:05.160 --> 08:09.160
Because I realized that I'm still hurt and
angry from all the times you cheated on me.

08:09.240 --> 08:11.080
Okay? And that is why
I kissed that guy.

08:11.160 --> 08:13.160
