08:13.240 --> 08:15.960
I'm sayin',
I'm not sorry.

08:19.800 --> 08:21.640
I'm not sorry!

08:23.120 --> 08:25.560
Come on!

08:28.120 --> 08:30.840
Look, now I know
why I cheated.

08:30.920 --> 08:34.440
You need to read this <i>Cosmo</i>
and find out why you did.

08:34.520 --> 08:36.799
I ripped out the boob pictures,
so don't bother looking.

08:41.320 --> 08:43.360
Hey, Donna, uh,
would you like a hot dog?

08:43.440 --> 08:45.400
Um, maybe half.

08:50.280 --> 08:52.120
Whoa, man,
you carry a knife?

08:52.200 --> 08:57.680
