but I'm the one who's prepared.

09:08.640 --> 09:10.880
He's like a gladiator.

09:14.360 --> 09:17.280
Okay, that's it. I'm bringing out
the big guns. Oh, yeah.

09:17.360 --> 09:19.240
I'm introducing him
to my folks.

09:21.120 --> 09:24.760
Oh, hey, Mom, meet Casey.
This is Donna's new boyfriend.

09:29.640 --> 09:34.720
Well, you're certainly not a girl!

09:37.320 --> 09:39.360
Nice to meet you,
Mrs. Forman.

09:39.440 --> 09:43.720
You know, you couldn't have picked a prettier
day to win a year's supply of hot dogs.

09:47.640 --> 09:49.960
Yeah, sure is a hot dog.

09:54.520 --> 09:56.360
Mom!

09:56.440 --> 10:00.640
Sorry, honey, it's just...
He's just...

10:02.760 --> 10:05.880
I am sure
you are much smarter.

10:09.400 --> 10:14.160
Kitty, the idiot neighbors
drank all my beer.

10:14.240 --> 10:17.120
Uh-oh. You're in a bad mood.
Hey, meet Casey.

10:18.480 --> 10:20.360
Pleasure, sir.

10:20.400 --> 10:22.560
Hey, maybe I can help.

10:22.600 --> 10:25.720
I always keep an spare case
of beer in the Trans Am.

10:25.800 --> 10:27.920
Little tip I picked up
in the army.

10:32.000 --> 10:34.720
I don't know.
Seems like a pretty good kid.

10:34.760 --> 10:37.640
Uh-huh.

10:37.680 --> 10:39.640
So, you and Casey, huh?

10:39.720 --> 10:42.240
Look, Hyde, whatever you heard
about Casey, he's changed now.

10:42.280 --> 10:44.640
He's... He's mature.

10:44.680 --> 10:47.120
Oh, yeah.
He's real mature.

10:47.200 --> 10:49.040
Well, I like him!

10:49.120 --> 10:51.800
We're together, and if you can't deal
with that, then you can just go to hell!

10:51.880 --> 10:55.160
Hey, that's not barbecue language,
young lady!

10:58.120 --> 11:01.600
Here's that beer, sir.
I got a soda for the minor.

11:05.080 --> 11:09.360
Now, you make sure
to drink that real slow...

11:09.440 --> 11:12.160
'cause I don't want you
to get a tummy ache, little guy.

11:17.000 --> 11:20.840
Well, that's thoughtful.

11:22.600 --> 11:25.080
Yeah, he cramps up easy.

11:32.700 --> 11:36.060
Casey and Donna, man.

11:36.140 --> 11:39.020
Hey, remember when we were 12?
We didn't even like girls yet.

11:41.500 --> 11:44.660
I liked girls
when I was 12.

11:44.700 --> 11:48.020
Yeah, I was happy to stay at home
Friday night in my underwear...

11:48.100 --> 11:50.540
just tossin'
a football to myself.

11:56.540 --> 11:58.700
Yeah, never did that either.

12:00.860 --> 12:05.780
Well, at least I gave it
my best shot, right?

12:05.820 --> 12:11.540
If Donna loves Casey and not me,
then, I mean, I guess it's over.

12:13.220 --> 12:17.020
Wha... Forman,
you can't give up.

12:17.100 --> 12:19.940
Okay, look. Who knows what's
gonna happen with me and Jackie.

12:20.020 --> 12:22.620
But what you
and Donna had?

12:22.700 --> 12:24.860
That was, like, real.

12:26.300 --> 12:30.100
And I'm telling you, as his brother...
Look, Casey is bad news.

12:30.140 --> 12:33.780
He's either gonna get bored and split,
or something worse is gonna happen.

12:33.860 --> 12:36.660
So, you gotta
do something.

12:39.300 --> 12:41.500
Hey, since when did
you get all serious?

12:44.220 --> 12:46.380
Been reading <i>Cosmo.</i>

12:52.220 --> 12:55.220
It's very educational.

12:55.300 --> 12:58.660
Yeah. I never realized how much
plumbing girls had down there.

13:00.660 --> 13:04.300
Like, there's this diagram,
and it's like a map of Six Flags.

13:07.460 --> 13:11.340
Okay, everyone.
Here's lunch.

13:12.300 --> 13:14.420
Hot dog soup!

13:15.700 --> 13:18.020
No more hot dogs!

13:18.100 --> 13:19.940
I'll just eat
the grilled cheese.

13:20.020 --> 13:22.820
You mean, grilled cheese
with hot dogs!

13:25.180 --> 13:27.580
Kitty, for God's sakes...

13:27.660 --> 13:31.500
I ate 14 hot dogs yesterday!

13:31.580 --> 13:33.980
Well, what do you want me to do, Red?
They're everywhere.

13:34.060 --> 13:36.300
They're a curse
on this house!

13:36.380 --> 13:39.220
Oh, fine.
Let's make some calls.

13:39.300 --> 13:42.420
Maybe we can unload
the damn things on a nursery school.

13:44.860 --> 13:48.020
You guys, I have let this thing
with Casey go way too far.

13:48.100 --> 13:50.580
Yeah, no kidding.
Donna's pretty far gone.

13:50.660 --> 13:53.140
She's starting to lash out
at people at barbecues.

13:53.180 --> 13:55.100
You gotta
kick his ass, man!

13:55.140 --> 13:58.260
