with his fists.

13:58.300 --> 14:01.900
He's a special boy who must beat him
with his special strengths.

14:03.900 --> 14:07.540
Now, let's think.
What is Eric's special strengths?

14:10.660 --> 14:13.300
Welcome back to TV's
favorite game show...

14:13.380 --> 14:16.100
<i>Get Into That Box!</i>

