16:02.300 --> 16:04.980
Well, we're off to
a nice start.

16:05.060 --> 16:07.420
Shall we move on
to second base?

16:15.900 --> 16:18.380
Ay, no.

16:20.580 --> 16:24.660
Guess what. I read your little
"everything's my fault" article...

16:24.740 --> 16:27.420
and I realized
why I cheated.

16:27.500 --> 16:29.460
Remember the first time
I kissed Pam Macy?

16:29.540 --> 16:33.460
- Behind the gym?
- And <i>in</i> the gym, and in her car.

16:34.540 --> 16:36.660
But, anyway...

16:36.700 --> 16:41.140
Earlier that day, I didn't have
any money to buy you Tater Tots.

16:41.220 --> 16:45.380
You said that I'd never be able to
support you, 'cause I wasn't smart enough.

16:45.460 --> 16:51.180
