18:27.340 --> 18:29.460
Oh. Well,
I gotta go too.

18:29.540 --> 18:31.420
Hey, Pinciotti.

18:34.900 --> 18:36.660
Love ya.

18:36.700 --> 18:38.580
Oh, well, I...

18:41.780 --> 18:44.340
Thank you.

18:44.380 --> 18:47.580
Okay, well I'll, uh,
I'll see you later.

18:51.060 --> 18:54.420
You see, Forman,
it's just words.

18:55.420 --> 18:57.380
You don't have to mean it.

19:00.660 --> 19:06.100
