Pow!

19:46.180 --> 19:48.060
Good.

19:48.100 --> 19:51.060
Because thanks to his stupid advice,
Rhonda dumped me.

19:51.140 --> 19:53.580
I tried to steal third,
but she blocked me...

19:53.660 --> 19:56.540
and choked me.

19:56.620 --> 19:59.540
Now there is
no more baseball for Fez.

19:59.580 --> 20:01.460
It's back to handball.

20:03.100 --> 20:06.420
Girls, man.
They'll make you miserable.

20:07.660 --> 20:09.540
Well, I got a date.

20:09.620 --> 20:11.620
"Tho" long, "thuckerth!"

